                                        <ol class="mb-0">
                                            <li class="mb-2">Get your claim started quickly by using <a href="{{ path('claim') }}">our online portal</a></li>
                                            <li class="mb-2">Our UK based claims team will review your claim and call you with a request for any further details or documents (if necessary). We aim to do this within a matter of business hours</li>
                                            <li class="mb-2">Once your claim is approved, we take your excess payment over the phone and aim to repair or replace your phone within 24-72 hours. Some repairs can take longer (e.g. water damage) but we will be as fast as possible</li>
